parameters:
\nc<Saki>Handcuffs... I ended up receiving them after all... I wonder
if there will be an opportunity to use them. Maybe this?

\nc<Saki>I need to unlock it and then press the blue button, right?
Here goes.

\nc<Saki>There doesn't seem to be any particular problem around
here... So I just need to report back and that's it?
\nc<Security Guard 1>The alarm has stopped. Was there any trouble?
\nc<Security Guard 1>Alright. Then, take a quick patrol around once more.
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Wah! You startled me... Are you an employee?
\nc<Employee 1>Ah, yes. Are you from the security company?
\nc<Employee?2>So the security companies are hiring succubi now...

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Haha, it seems so... By the way, why is everyone wearing
masks?

\nc<Thief 1>(Shoot, I forgot to take it off!) This is... part of our
social distancing measures.
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Oh, I see... Well then, I'll be on my way here.
\nc<Thief 1>Ah, yes. Thank you for your hard work!
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>(I need to get back and report this quickly...) Huh...!?
